menus scripting language for creating the ui thing

syntax concept:

```
// Initializers specify properties in a config file sorta format
Menu menu {
    Button text {
        text = "Hello World!";
        x = 0;
        y = 0;
    };

    Button ok {
        text = "ok";
        x = 7;
        y = 1;
        onpress() {
            int; // interupt (pass control to the shell script, then it does stuff then resumes here)
        };
    };
};

main() {
    display menu;
};
```